  "Term": "俯首之刻",
  "Color": "",
  "Placeholder": [],
  "TermTitle": "俯首之刻",
  "TermDesc": "<span style=\"color:#ffd12f;\" class=\"font-bold\">俯首之刻</span>持续期间时间暂时停止，<span style=\"color:#ffd12f;\" class=\"font-bold\">不能切换角色</span>，仅能施放<span style=\"color:#ffd12f;\" class=\"font-bold\">赫日威临·烈阳</span>、<span style=\"color:#ffd12f;\" class=\"font-bold\">赫日威临·不朽者之肃</span>、<span style=\"color:#ffd12f;\" class=\"font-bold\">闪避</span>，处于空中状态时可以施放<span style=\"color:#ffd12f;\" class=\"font-bold\">空中攻击</span>。<br>·<span style=\"color:#ffd12f;\" class=\"font-bold\">俯首之刻</span>期间，<span style=\"color:#ffd12f;\" class=\"font-bold\">短按普攻</span>或<span style=\"color:#ffd12f;\" class=\"font-bold\">长按普攻</span>可施放<span style=\"color:#ffd12f;\" class=\"font-bold\">赫日威临·烈阳</span>。可在水面行走且不消耗耐力。<br>·<span style=\"color:#ffd12f;\" class=\"font-bold\">俯首之刻</span>结束时自动施放<span style=\"color:#ffd12f;\" class=\"font-bold\">赫日威临·不朽者之肃</span>。<br>·若进行<span style=\"color:#ffd12f;\" class=\"font-bold\">场景、玩法、或功能交互</span>时，将强制结束<span style=\"color:#ffd12f;\" class=\"font-bold\">俯首之刻</span>，且不会自动施放<span style=\"color:#ffd12f;\" class=\"font-bold\">赫日威临·不朽者之肃</span>。"
}